Title: Love journey with half girlfriend
DateModified: '2018-02-10'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/love-journey-with-half-girlfriend
SetInCountry: India
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: ANil Kasana
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "Its was month of October . I was preparing for government job in delhi . I\
  \ got notification that a recuitment rally for army will held in madaya pardesh\
  \ ,a beautiful state of india . I didn't notify my faimly about this . I managed\
  \ money with help of friend. And went to rally . We have to qualify race pf 1600m.\
  \ But i stood last second . I was disappointed and pack my bag and get ready to\
  \ move back to delhi . I take a passenger train huge rush was there . But i managed\
  \ to get a window seat after passing two station . A girl with two bag come come\
  \ near to me and asked for seat . She managed to get seat near me . She was beautiful\
  \ and seems 23old . I thought she would not speak to me . But after some time she\
  \ took out her lunch box and she offer me food .i was feeling so hungry but denied\
  \ . My hunger was on peak . She once again offer me . I can't stop my self and i\
  \ move my hand toward her tiffan . She gave me two chapatis . Now i feel bit relaxed\
  \ .\n ..cont."
